== TAJMILT i  KATEB  YASIN ==

'''NEĞMA N MEDDEN IRKEL'''
Sɣur Saɛid Cemax,

TAFSUT, U°14, ibrir 1990, Tizi-Wezzu. 

Ayen akk ɣef tezza tasa-k d Neğma i k-yeooan asmi i tt-tebɣiv. Teslul-d times ur ssexsayen igefran di taffa n yesɣaren yezgan i rekku. Tendeḥ tmes, reqqen lekwaɣeḍ, acɛal d aseggas tura, keç tettwaliḍ deg ujajiḥ udem n Neğma i yetteftutusen ciṭ ciṭ, armi d asmi i ifukk acku aɣembabu n wabbu iɣumm tagnit igenni. Iwwet deg wul-ik iɣisi amek akka Neğma ur tt-teseiḍ ara deg wexxa-ik. Yeɣli-d fell-ak usemmiḍ yal ass, ḥala lexyal-is i dyeqqimen yettarra-d cwiṭ n wezɣal deg wul. Ass-a ula d netta ikka akin i ééerb n wabbu.

Tebɣiv ad truḍ, d acu a d-yexdem imeîîi ? ɣas ad truḍ ihenwiḍen, maççi a d-tuɣal, ifat tôuê, tûaê-d i wayeḍ.

Tettafev ddwa $as akken xerden meôôa deg ugeôôu n lkif i tessa$ayev, si tikelt $er tayev, i tetteksev lxiq u tettafev tiéeî i ddunit tameréagut. Tikwal tettezziv $er tissit, têemmlev ccrab, akken iêemmel llufan ayefki n yemma-s... Teddrev agiôôu d teqra e t d imeddukal-ik n yal ass.

Mi tunnav zzhu-agi wer d-yettara lferê i deg i d-tekkrev zik, tettezziv $er rregmat : widen tessarsev-asen armi ur sen-teooiv ara. Tegliv ula s tajaddit. Qebluî acu t-id-yewwin a d-igger iman-is deg ayen ur t-yaenin ? Ina$ immut ? Acu i wumi a itennev nnig uqerru nne$ am igider aberkan yettnadi melmi a yeédem $ef kra ? Yessawev s lec$al-is yewwi Neoma, ur yettaooa ara taswiet i deg ara yu$al ufud s avar. Zzehî s wayes i d-yemme$ tecba tin n wegdud seg i d-yu$ aéar mi d-teddun yemnayen akken ad nna$en d yemnekcamen i d-yessawven. Neoma mi tt-êaôôen lejdud $er lêeôma nnsen, nnven-as leêyuv n wabbu : mi yerra wemdan ad asen-yezger ad iûree, ad i$li $er tegnit. Maca imnekcamen êercen $ran yal timucuha, iéuran n tagut ufan-ten, éran melmi yer$a lebêeô. Ma d keç wer te$riv, wer tnudav, wer teériv : tettedduv kan am uegellil, yal ti$emmar i $er terriv ad teddariv ad tt-id-ddun i yiman-ik, tettruv tettecvev ur tettnekkarev ara. Imnakcamen jban-d si yal tamurt am yemsewqen, wwin-d ukk leêruz d ttbaxuô : yal w amek i d-yenna tamacahut. Imezdaɣen n tmurt zgan d i$riben, terra-ten temeayt d ibeôôaniyen. Ff$en izuɣar, kecmen idurar d uneéruf : din i suven tirget i d-yeqqimen seg wes$ar nni ireqqen acêal d lqern tura. Slalen-d ajajiê seg iɣed, yal wa yeddem asafu, rzan $ef wid iêeôôen akal, nnan-asen : ‘Ffɣet ! ur awen-nessekra, ur awen-nezzenz'... Imnekcamen bɣan akk Neğma a tt-seun ger ifassen nsen. Akken yeb$u ad mm$en a tt-id-îîfen, $as ad ssiwven s aya, allaɣ-is ireggel d awez$i a t-kesben ! Wa yettaooa-tt i wayev, d tameɣbunt ; wid i tt-yeb$an, bɣan kan i wayen a ddmen seg-s. Tewwev-ik-id keç, kksen-ak-tt lejdud imi ur as-tezmirev ara. Ayen ur tezmire'ḍ ? D keç i yeéran ! Ladɣa ula d keç ur ak-yefri ara usteqsi-agi, tezziv tefriv-t s ccôab akd lkif. Keç ur ak-tefri, tufiv-as aqerru swayes a tefru deg imal.

Teslalev-d asefru, yemlal-d gma-s, nudan-d ameddakel, ssalin zzmam. Zzmamat dduklen, slan-d akk medden : yeffeɣ wawal, yelêa di tmura. Nnan lɣaci : ayen yedder wagi, neddrit akk... ziɣ llan wid yessufuɣen tirga n tilawt i deg nettemxebbav d isefra. Neoma tedder d tayemmat-nneɣ, weltmat-neɣ tameîîut-nneɣ, tella d Lezzayer tamurt. Tella d tameddurt i daɣ-yezduklen. Trefdev allen-ik tessakdev, tamu$li-k tamezwarut temlal-d allen n Neoma yeqqlen d asmekti deg walla$, tecfiv fell-as ccfaya n win meééiyen. ɣas nettat ahat tettu imi tkecmem tagelda n tatut, tamu$li n wass-n d tin yettnadin allen-is, tettcerrig igemmaven, tettmagar icelyaven tetteddu deg uneéruf anda ijdi iɣumm igenwan.Tetteddu seg lewvayat d izuɣar mebla tilas. Tetteddu ger lmujat n yill cerrgen lembabeô yessemlalen timura n wemval.

Tamu$li yersen di Neoma d tin yeddan d iseggasen $as zerrin ass deffir wass, Neğma d itri i d-ibanen deg igenwan ger watmaten-is ttalasen akk deg-s medden, $as yalwa yesea-tt i yiman-is ...

Nessaram-ak Rreḥma a Yasin !

